15
00:04:57,980 --> 00:04:59,413
You should change.

16
00:04:59,940 --> 00:05:00,417
Come.

17
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:06,816
Show me.

18
00:05:08,860 --> 00:05:10,339
I'm ashamed of it.

19
00:05:18,860 --> 00:05:20,293
How did it happen?

20
00:05:23,420 --> 00:05:26,412
My girlfriend's father
slammed a car door on it

21
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:28,659
right after high school exams.

22
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:31,131
I had just passed my piano exam

23
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:32,933
that day.

24
00:05:33,940 --> 00:05:35,134
I fainted.

25
00:07:22,100 --> 00:07:22,771
Papa...

26
00:07:25,700 --> 00:07:26,849
What are you listening to?

27
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:29,372
The same as always.

28
00:07:31,780 --> 00:07:32,815
I woke up.

29
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:38,979
Tell Antek I have to leave.
He'll be sad.

30
00:07:40,140 --> 00:07:40,856
And you?

31
00:07:43,500 --> 00:07:45,331
I'm sorry Auntie's not well.

32
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:47,178
But I'm glad she called.

33
00:07:48,660 --> 00:07:49,854
You want to go there?

34
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:51,930
Yes.

35
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:53,694
I like Krakow.

36
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:57,370
Did you ask her to call?

37
00:07:58,580 --> 00:07:59,517
No.

38
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,792
I have a strange feeling.

39
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:12,231
I feel that I'm not alone.

40
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,599
Not alone, how?

41
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:20,276
That I'm not alone in the world.

42
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:23,554
You aren't.

43
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,116
I don't know.

44
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,596
What do I really want, Papa?

45
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:56,875
I don't know.

46
00:08:58,160 --> 00:09:00,037
Probably quite a lot of things.

47
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,234
A blond boy?

48
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,031
Yes.

49
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:14,232
You've slept with him?

50
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,188
Yes.

51
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:18,796
Tell me.

52
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:27,574
The last time...

53
00:10:29,340 --> 00:10:30,932
