103
00:20:21,080 --> 00:20:22,672
You look fantastic, Auntie.

104
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:24,875
Really.

105
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:27,310
Fantastic.

106
00:20:28,080 --> 00:20:31,152
If you had played cards all night

107
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:33,595
and drunk vodka,
you'd be equally beautiful.

108
00:20:36,900 --> 00:20:38,492
How did things go?

109
00:20:38,740 --> 00:20:39,490
Fine.

110
00:20:43,300 --> 00:20:45,768
I'm even afraid it went too well.

111
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:37,371
I was wondering
if you'd notice me.

112
00:21:41,740 --> 00:21:43,537
Were you following me a long time?

113
00:21:44,740 --> 00:21:46,059
A long time.

114
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:51,397
My aunt said you had called.

115
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:54,598
I spoke with my father.

116
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:56,553
He said you were fine.

117
00:21:57,560 --> 00:21:58,276
I'm alive.

118
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:01,790
I thought I would

119
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:04,558
