to tell you I love you.

124
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:29,236
I'm staying at the Holiday Inn.

125
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:31,832
If you want to tell me anything,
call me.

126
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:34,072
Room 287.

127
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:56,151
Antek!

128
00:22:57,760 --> 00:22:59,318
