146
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:14,995
I don't know why.
It's as if I were grieving.

147
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:18,475
For someone?

148
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:21,795
I don't know.

149
00:31:25,280 --> 00:31:27,236
