150
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:28,350
No.

151
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:05,470
Are you all right?

152
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:10,593
Can I stay a while?

153
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:11,871
